Partner Service Representative (PSR)  -
Partner Service Representative (PSR)
Responsibilities
Developing good customer relationship with the business partners.Inputting data into the software system and answers telephone calls plus must be willing to do administrative tasks.Assisting business partners when needed.  Requirement :Minimum S1 degree minimum and we need experienced staff only and must have work experienced of minimum 5 years as office admin or marketing services.Male or female can apply but must have good attitude, good and friendly look, good etiquette, and hard working.Tardiness, hard working , honest, willing to work over the office hours and must have responsibility.Must be willing to speak English, Bahasa Indonesia, and speaking Mandarin is a PLUS.Ability to work as a team (Must be a team player and work as a group to help each other to complete the task. Must be willing to learn or be coachable in order to succeed).Having a strong passion, honest, adaptable and ability to work under pressure at all time.
